 
There is a strong smell of gas pervading the air.
Small glittering pool.
The water cools you down.
Switch.
The torches Ignite and so does the swamp gas.
Hundreds of snakes crawl out of the floor and bite you.
Swamp gas forces you back couching and gagging.
"You drink the water, with no effect."
The switch does not work.
Hundreds of snakes crawl out of the floor and bite you. 
A voice hisses -Walk the path of the snake-.
"A voice whispers -I am the spirit of the swamp, congratulations, take what you may and leave in peace-"
